<p>Best part of getting a foreign drivers license is actually getting pulled over! They have no idea what to do with the damn thing, so they just let you go (I say this from experience, having a Japanese license and no American one). </p>
<p>Downside: Buying alcohol or getting into bars unless you want to carry your passport. Bouncers and bartenders have seen it all, and aren&#8217;t easily convinced by a foreign drivers license.</p>
